<br>
For a large race warrior when we say slam or bash...we really just mean slam. Forget the whole shield thing. <br>
<br>
But yes, you are right. Bash works fine in doggy form (with a shield), slam (which doesn't use a shield) does not work in doggy form.<br>
<br>
While at high levels kick and slam may seem to be on equal footing...slam actually has a considerably higher skill cap then kick does...of course, this is mute when you are getting a huge attack bonus from doggy form. <br>
<br>
